  & (x, y, z) & \longrightarrow & (x-y+z, 2y+z-1)
\end{array}
\begin{array}{cccc}
J:& \mathbb{R}^3 & \rightarrow  & \mathbb{R}^2 \\
  & (x, y, z) & \longrightarrow & (x-y, 3z+2x)
\end{array} $

